---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section id="getting-started">
  <p class="section-label">// getting started</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Up and running in seconds.</h2>
  <p class="section-desc">No installation required to try it out.</p>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">01</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Run without installing</h3>
        <p>Use <code>npx</code> to run mdwow directly — no global install needed.</p>
        <div class="term-block">
          <span class="prompt">$</span> npx mdwow-cli README.md
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">02</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Or install globally</h3>
        <p>Install once, use everywhere as the <code>mdwow</code> command.</p>
        <div class="term-block">
          <span class="prompt">$</span> npm install -g mdwow-cli<br />
          <span class="prompt">$</span> mdwow README.md
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">03</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Point it at any Markdown file</h3>
        <p>Works with any <code>.md</code> file — local docs, notes, or project READMEs.</p>
        <div class="term-block">
          <span class="prompt">$</span> mdwow docs/guide.md<br />
          <span class="prompt">$</span> mdwow ~/notes/todo.md<br />
          <span class="prompt">$</span> mdwow CHANGELOG.md
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prereq">
    <span class="prompt">#</span> Requires Node.js 18 or later
  </div>

  <div class="dev-cta">
    <p>Building or contributing to mdwow?</p>
    <a href={`${base}dev`} class="btn">View Developer Guide →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3rem 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--border);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    padding-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .step-content > p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .prereq {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-card);
  }

  .prereq .prompt {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .dev-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-card);
  }

  .dev-cta p {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .step { grid-template-columns: 2rem 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .step-num { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .dev-cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
